As soon as I'm finished, I'll talk to you.

815
00:55:03,967 --> 00:55:06,736
(dramatic music)

816
00:55:36,566 --> 00:55:38,600
Keep the faith.

817
00:55:38,601 --> 00:55:40,169
Please, have a seat.

818
00:55:40,170 --> 00:55:41,171
- Thank you.

819
00:55:42,005 --> 00:55:46,141
- What is so urgent you
need to talk to me about?

820
00:55:46,142 --> 00:55:48,110
- Christopher Hayes spoke
to you some time ago

821
00:55:48,111 --> 00:55:51,613
of a certain recollection
of memories he's having?

822
00:55:51,614 --> 00:55:52,915
- I remember.

823
00:55:52,916 --> 00:55:55,718
Christopher is a man who is
aware of his surroundings

824
00:55:55,719 --> 00:55:57,252
when most are asleep.

825
00:55:57,253 --> 00:56:00,889
He's developed a sensibility
to connect with his past life,

826
00:56:00,890 --> 00:56:02,257
therefore avoiding the pitfalls

827
00:56:02,258 --> 00:56:04,193
most of us fall into.

828
00:56:04,194 --> 00:56:07,529
- I need to know if I'm
the one he keeps seeing.

829
00:56:07,530 --> 00:56:09,531
- I can't tell you that.

830
00:56:09,532 --> 00:56:10,599
- Why?

831
00:56:10,600 --> 00:56:13,068
- I never talk to others about
anyone else but themselves.

832
00:56:13,069 --> 00:56:15,471
I do it out of respect and courtesy.

833
00:56:15,472 --> 00:56:16,505
- Please?

834
00:56:16,506 --> 00:56:17,506
I need your help.

835
00:56:18,641 --> 00:56:19,709
- I could read you.

836
00:56:20,610 --> 00:56:21,610
- Okay.

837
00:56:26,649 --> 00:56:28,150
- Do you believe in fate?

838
00:56:28,151 --> 00:56:29,151
- Yes.

839
00:56:30,153 --> 00:56:31,954
- You're about to get married.

840
00:56:31,955 --> 00:56:33,122
- Yes.

841
00:56:33,123 --> 00:56:34,723
Yes, I am.

842
00:56:34,724 --> 00:56:36,625
- You have found your soulmate.

843
00:56:36,626 --> 00:56:38,227
- I have.

844
00:56:38,228 --> 00:56:40,029
- You two love each other very much.

845
00:56:40,897 --> 00:56:42,265
Fate has town you apart.

846
00:56:43,099 --> 00:56:45,401
However, you must unite with destiny,

847
00:56:45,402 --> 00:56:46,436
that is your fate.

848
00:56:47,704 --> 00:56:49,004
- Thank you.

849
00:56:49,005 --> 00:56:50,639
- Be in tune with your spirit

850
00:56:50,640 --> 00:56:52,408
and you will see how everything works out

851
00:56:52,409 --> 00:56:54,209
for you and yours.

852
00:56:54,210 --> 00:56:57,479
In two stories, there are
usually three realities.

853
00:56:57,480 --> 00:57:00,916
Yours, theirs, and what really happens.

854
00:57:00,917 --> 00:57:03,719
But who's to say what's
happening from what's not?

855
00:57:03,720 --> 00:57:06,021
We might not be able to
control circumstance,

856
00:57:06,022 --> 00:57:09,159
but we can control our actions
and act on our feelings.

857
00:57:10,560 --> 00:57:12,227
You're hurting inside,

858
00:57:12,228 --> 00:57:14,063
but don't let destiny pass you by.

859
00:57:15,532 --> 00:57:17,801
I think you'll be able
to figure the rest out.

860
00:57:19,502 --> 00:57:20,703
You've been here before.

861
00:57:22,205 --> 00:57:24,106
Go and have a happy life
with your loved ones.

862
00:57:24,107 --> 00:57:25,108
- Thank you.

863
00:57:38,121 --> 00:57:40,790
(toy box music)

864
00:57:43,393 --> 00:57:44,394
- I'm sorry.

