00:58:10,253 --> 00:58:12,488
and this is what I do to her?

875
00:58:12,489 --> 00:58:14,590
I just hope that she
can forgive me some day.

876
00:58:14,591 --> 00:58:18,961
- I don't think you're
resolving anything by leaving.

877
00:58:18,962 --> 00:58:21,630
- My father was right.

878
00:58:21,631 --> 00:58:23,299
I'm not good enough.

879
00:58:24,267 --> 00:58:25,267
- What do you mean?

880
00:58:27,637 --> 00:58:29,671
Do you know how many
people's lives you touch

881
00:58:29,672 --> 00:58:30,672
with your writing?

882
00:58:35,144 --> 00:58:36,144
Like mine.

883
00:58:38,147 --> 00:58:40,182
- You read my article?

884
00:58:40,183 --> 00:58:41,084
- Yes.

885
00:58:41,085 --> 00:58:43,285
I had to see for myself
what you were talking about,

886
00:58:43,286 --> 00:58:45,387
so I went to see her.

887
00:58:45,388 --> 00:58:48,290
- [Christopher] What happened?

888
00:58:48,291 --> 00:58:52,094
- We spoke, and I think
you're right about this lady,

889
00:58:52,095 --> 00:58:53,662
there's something very real about her,

890
00:58:53,663 --> 00:58:56,833
and I believe her.

891
00:58:58,568 --> 00:59:01,136
- Well, I'm not so sure about any of this.

892
00:59:01,137 --> 00:59:03,873
(dramatic music)

893
00:59:16,052 --> 00:59:18,888
The cab should be here any minute.

894
00:59:26,462 --> 00:59:29,398
- I hate to see you go, I feel
like this is all my fault.

895
00:59:29,399 --> 00:59:30,966
- We can't keep blaming ourselves,

896
00:59:30,967 --> 00:59:32,634
what happened is done.

897
00:59:32,635 --> 00:59:34,870
- I'm glad to see that you...

898
00:59:34,871 --> 00:59:36,872
You know, we were drunk and-

