- It's pretty clear what I saw.

900
00:59:39,375 --> 00:59:40,576
- I believe you.

901
00:59:40,577 --> 00:59:42,745
- No, I don't want you or Ben to leave.

902
00:59:47,684 --> 00:59:49,585
I thought about this.

903
00:59:49,586 --> 00:59:50,420
- And what?

904
00:59:50,420 --> 00:59:51,254
What do you want me to do?

905
00:59:51,255 --> 00:59:53,322
I'll do whatever you want.

906
00:59:53,323 --> 00:59:55,357
- You're the only man I have ever loved

907
00:59:55,358 --> 00:59:56,459
