01:00:06,536 --> 01:00:08,204
- What about my father?

913
01:00:09,072 --> 01:00:12,375
- You're a part of me,
and I'm a part of you.

914
01:00:13,443 --> 01:00:16,813
I would never do anything
to hurt you, never.

915
01:00:18,581 --> 01:00:19,581
It's all my fault.

916
01:00:19,582 --> 01:00:22,117
I think I've caused enough
trouble around here.

917
01:00:22,118 --> 01:00:23,118
- No, wait.

918
01:00:28,891 --> 01:00:31,426
I've thought about this.

919
01:00:31,427 --> 01:00:33,228
You came here to walk me down the aisle

920
01:00:33,229 --> 01:00:35,932
to the only man I have ever
loved in my entire life.

921
01:00:38,134 --> 01:00:40,870
And that's what I want you to do.

922
01:00:44,941 --> 01:00:45,941
Okay?

923
01:00:47,710 --> 01:00:49,612
- We can't pretend this didn't happen.

924
01:00:52,315 --> 01:00:53,483
- It happened.

925
01:00:56,686 --> 01:00:58,154
I don't have anyone left.

926
01:01:00,390 --> 01:01:01,824
You both are my family.

927
01:01:03,760 --> 01:01:06,294
And I'm not about to give up on you,

928
01:01:06,295 --> 01:01:08,296
either one of you.

